        <abstract> 
<p>Discusses text of <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi>.</p> 
            <p>Compares Eocene and modern climates.</p>
            <p>Mentions Hooker’s view of his geographical [distribution] chapters.</p>
            <p>Asks CL’s opinion of his statements on distribution during "glacial and preceding warmer periods".</p>
            <p>Mentions chapters on geological record and embryology.</p>
        </abstract>
